[size=4][b]Heads-up[/b][/size]

[size=3]This one is experimental. The mod takes an automatic backup of your save file before every edit, but you should still back up your whole [code]Saves[/code] folder before any major change. If something goes sideways, please file a bug report with [code]LogOutput.log[/code] attached.[/size]

[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Re-open the character creator on any save from the load-game screen. Fix the haircut, swap the name, redo the eye colour — without starting over.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]Edit any saved character[/b] — appearance and name from the load-game screen. Click the edit button next to a save and the character creator opens with that character's current look loaded.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Auto-backup before each edit[/b] — the mod copies your save file to a timestamped backup before writing changes, so a bad edit can be reverted by hand.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Open save folder shortcut[/b] — the configuration menu has a button that opens your Sun Haven save directory in Explorer for manual backups or restores.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/37]Easy Living[/url] — quick-save with a keybind makes recovering from a botched edit even easier.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/7]UI Scales[/url] — bumps up the dialogue portrait so your new look actually fills the conversation panel.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31]Keep Alive[/url] — keeps mods loaded between play sessions; recommended whenever you have any mods installed.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30][size=3]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/size][/url]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Compatibility[/b][/size]

[size=3]Built and tested against the latest Steam build of Sun Haven.[/size]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...\steamapps\common\Sun Haven\BepInEx\plugins[/code][/size]

